{"version":1,"cues":[{"start":1,"end":8.967,"text":"欢迎来到这项杀手级功能！克隆整个生产仓库，无论大小，都不会破坏任何东西。","words":[{"start":1,"end":8.967,"char":[0,36]}]},{"start":9.741,"end":12.954,"text":"一个父仓库可以扇出任意数量的独立克隆。每一个","words":[{"start":9.741,"end":12.954,"char":[0,22]}]},{"start":12.954,"end":16.167,"text":"fork","words":[{"start":12.954,"end":16.167,"char":[0,4]}]},{"start":16.167,"end":19.38,"text":"都是它自己独立的环境，与原始仓库并排运行。","words":[{"start":16.167,"end":19.38,"char":[0,21]}]},{"start":20.154,"end":25.849,"text":"想象一下分享一个文件夹链接。无论文件夹是小还是巨大，链接都是同样轻量的东西，fork","words":[{"start":20.154,"end":25.849,"char":[0,42]}]},{"start":25.849,"end":31.543,"text":"的工作原理也是如此。","words":[{"start":25.849,"end":31.543,"char":[0,10]}]},{"start":32.331,"end":36.03,"text":"1 GB、100","words":[{"start":32.331,"end":34.18,"char":[0,1]},{"start":34.18,"end":36.03,"char":[2,8]}]},{"start":36.03,"end":39.729,"text":"GB、1 TB：fork","words":[{"start":36.03,"end":37.879,"char":[0,4]},{"start":37.879,"end":39.729,"char":[5,12]}]},{"start":39.729,"end":41.578,"text":"的表现都一样。仓库大小不会影响这一过程。","words":[{"start":39.729,"end":41.578,"char":[0,20]}]},{"start":44.849,"end":47.4,"text":"让我们","words":[{"start":44.849,"end":47.4,"char":[0,3]}]},{"start":47.4,"end":49.952,"text":"fork","words":[{"start":47.4,"end":49.952,"char":[0,4]}]},{"start":49.952,"end":52.503,"text":"这个仓库。一条命令克隆了一切，应用、数据库、配置文件，只用了几秒，无论仓库有多大都一样。1","words":[{"start":49.952,"end":52.503,"char":[0,45]}]},{"start":52.503,"end":55.054,"text":"GB、100","words":[{"start":52.503,"end":55.054,"char":[0,6]}]},{"start":55.054,"end":57.605,"text":"GB、1","words":[{"start":55.054,"end":57.605,"char":[0,4]}]},{"start":57.605,"end":60.157,"text":"TB，每次时间相同。","words":[{"start":57.605,"end":60.157,"char":[0,10]}]},{"start":63.157,"end":67.598,"text":"fork 完成。克隆已启动并运行，无论大小如何。","words":[{"start":63.157,"end":65.377,"char":[0,4]},{"start":65.377,"end":67.598,"char":[5,24]}]},{"start":70.917,"end":73.967,"text":"现在两个仓库并排运行。相同的机器，相同的磁盘，两个完全独立的环境。fork","words":[{"start":70.917,"end":73.967,"char":[0,37]}]},{"start":73.967,"end":77.017,"text":"有自己的容器、自己的文件系统和自己的","words":[{"start":73.967,"end":77.017,"char":[0,18]}]},{"start":77.017,"end":80.066,"text":"Docker","words":[{"start":77.017,"end":80.066,"char":[0,6]}]},{"start":80.066,"end":83.116,"text":"守护进程。","words":[{"start":80.066,"end":83.116,"char":[0,5]}]},{"start":86.116,"end":91.106,"text":"两个 repo，一个磁盘。相同的数据，其他一切都独立。","words":[{"start":86.116,"end":88.611,"char":[0,2]},{"start":88.611,"end":91.106,"char":[3,27]}]},{"start":94.442,"end":100.267,"text":"让我们来证明隔离性。在原始仓库中，我们的标记文件还在原来的位置。fork","words":[{"start":94.442,"end":100.267,"char":[0,36]}]},{"start":100.267,"end":106.093,"text":"的存在没有对父仓库造成任何影响。","words":[{"start":100.267,"end":106.093,"char":[0,16]}]},{"start":106.893,"end":109.897,"text":"原始文件还在。fork 没有触碰它。","words":[{"start":106.893,"end":108.395,"char":[0,11]},{"start":108.395,"end":109.897,"char":[12,18]}]},{"start":110.704,"end":115.145,"text":"父仓库就像太阳，你的","words":[{"start":110.704,"end":115.145,"char":[0,10]}]},{"start":115.145,"end":119.586,"text":"fork","words":[{"start":115.145,"end":119.586,"char":[0,4]}]},{"start":119.586,"end":124.026,"text":"是接收阳光的镜子。共享的基础保持不变，而你画在镜子上的一切只属于你自己。","words":[{"start":119.586,"end":124.026,"char":[0,36]}]},{"start":127.286,"end":130.615,"text":"现在让我们删除那个文件，但只在 fork","words":[{"start":127.286,"end":128.95,"char":[0,15]},{"start":128.95,"end":130.615,"char":[16,20]}]},{"start":130.615,"end":133.944,"text":"内部删除。在 fork","words":[{"start":130.615,"end":132.279,"char":[0,6]},{"start":132.279,"end":133.944,"char":[7,11]}]},{"start":133.944,"end":137.272,"text":"里它已经消失了，我们做了一个破坏性的操作，它留在了 fork","words":[{"start":133.944,"end":135.608,"char":[0,25]},{"start":135.608,"end":137.272,"char":[26,30]}]},{"start":137.272,"end":138.937,"text":"之内。","words":[{"start":137.272,"end":138.937,"char":[0,3]}]},{"start":139.737,"end":143.446,"text":"在 fork 中已消失。原始仓库保持不变。","words":[{"start":139.737,"end":140.973,"char":[0,1]},{"start":140.973,"end":142.21,"char":[2,6]},{"start":142.21,"end":143.446,"char":[7,21]}]},{"start":146.767,"end":150.563,"text":"回到原始仓库。标记文件还在这里，完好无损。原始仓库从不知道发生了什么。相同的镜像，独立的","words":[{"start":146.767,"end":150.563,"char":[0,44]}]},{"start":150.563,"end":154.36,"text":"Docker","words":[{"start":150.563,"end":154.36,"char":[0,6]}]},{"start":154.36,"end":158.156,"text":"守护进程，独立的文件系统。","words":[{"start":154.36,"end":158.156,"char":[0,13]}]},{"start":158.956,"end":161.647,"text":"依然在。fork 的隔离是真实的。","words":[{"start":158.956,"end":160.302,"char":[0,8]},{"start":160.302,"end":161.647,"char":[9,17]}]},{"start":164.937,"end":168.437,"text":"完成后，直接删除","words":[{"start":164.937,"end":168.437,"char":[0,8]}]},{"start":168.437,"end":171.938,"text":"fork。原始仓库保持原样。Fork、实验、破坏、删除，零风险。","words":[{"start":168.437,"end":171.938,"char":[0,32]}]},{"start":175.438,"end":179.565,"text":"fork 已移除。原始仓库与我们离开时一模一样。","words":[{"start":175.438,"end":177.502,"char":[0,4]},{"start":177.502,"end":179.565,"char":[5,24]}]},{"start":180.346,"end":184.839,"text":"一个","words":[{"start":180.346,"end":184.839,"char":[0,2]}]},{"start":184.839,"end":189.332,"text":"fork","words":[{"start":184.839,"end":189.332,"char":[0,4]}]},{"start":189.332,"end":193.825,"text":"就像在某一瞬间为父仓库拍下的定格照片。父仓库继续如河流般流动，但你的快照保持在拍摄时的样子。","words":[{"start":189.332,"end":193.825,"char":[0,46]}]},{"start":194.59,"end":198.226,"text":"一个 100 GB","words":[{"start":194.59,"end":195.802,"char":[0,2]},{"start":195.802,"end":197.014,"char":[3,6]},{"start":197.014,"end":198.226,"char":[7,9]}]},{"start":198.226,"end":201.862,"text":"仓库的五个 fork 在磁盘上加起来仍然只占约","words":[{"start":198.226,"end":199.438,"char":[0,5]},{"start":199.438,"end":200.65,"char":[6,10]},{"start":200.65,"end":201.862,"char":[11,23]}]},{"start":201.862,"end":205.499,"text":"100 GB。你只为每个 fork","words":[{"start":201.862,"end":203.075,"char":[0,3]},{"start":203.075,"end":204.287,"char":[4,12]},{"start":204.287,"end":205.499,"char":[13,17]}]},{"start":205.499,"end":206.711,"text":"中实际改变的字节付费。","words":[{"start":205.499,"end":206.711,"char":[0,11]}]},{"start":207.487,"end":210.694,"text":"fork","words":[{"start":207.487,"end":210.694,"char":[0,4]}]},{"start":210.694,"end":213.9,"text":"故意把密钥留在原地，这正是","words":[{"start":210.694,"end":213.9,"char":[0,13]}]},{"start":213.9,"end":217.107,"text":"“克隆生产环境而不破坏任何东西”","words":[{"start":213.9,"end":217.107,"char":[0,16]}]},{"start":217.107,"end":220.313,"text":"真正安全的原因。我们将在下个教程中正确配置它们！","words":[{"start":217.107,"end":220.313,"char":[0,24]}]}]}